body_html: @carlthome: Unfortunately, python -c 'import tensorflow as tf; sess = tf.Session(); sess.run(tf.square(0)); sess.close()' exhibits the same behavior, as does python -c $'import tensorflow as tf\nwith tf.Session() as sess: sess.run(tf.square(0))'.

body: @carlthome: Unfortunately, `python -c 'import tensorflow as tf; sess = tf.Session(); sess.run(tf.square(0)); sess.close()'` exhibits the same behavior, as does `python -c $'import tensorflow as tf\nwith tf.Session() as sess: sess.run(tf.square(0))'`.
